profile: Georgina Cut'n Clean Property Services strive to serve our customers with the most affordable, reliable and honest property care. In doing so we offer multiple lawn maintenance, Snow removal and other property maintenance packages for our customers to choose from.  We are a husband and wife that decided we wanted to help keep their community a beautiful and clean place to live for all that live here. Georgina Cut’n Clean Property Services is a family owned and operated local business with over 10 years of experience that specializes in residential lawn maintenance and Snow removal.
services:
- Snow removal 
- Lawn maintenance 
- Spring/Fall Cleanups 
- Gardens ( install, maintenance and cleanups) 
- Hedge/ Small tree trimming
- Lawn aeration 
- Lawn Fertilizing and seeding
payment_method: cash, E-transfer and Visa (with an additional 3% charge)

profile:
We are a Durham Region based Property Services Company! Specialized in All Residential and Commercial Grounds’ Needs.
 
We offer:
- Lawn Care top to bottom
- Service covers Cut , Edge/Trim , Bag , and Debris removal!
- Fertilization Options that ensure your lawn always looks and is at its BEST ! - Spring/Fall Lawn Clean up services !
- Hedge installation And Maintenance (Trimming, etc.)
- Minor and Major Grading
- Fence Installation
- Residential / Commercial Snow Removal
- Tree and Stump Removal 

We are fully insured up to $2m in liability.
